en_489741_0	Minister Johnston Fernando has pointed out that the work on the first quarter of the Southern Expressway from Matara to Hambantota will be completed and would be vested in the people before April this year.
en_489741_1	He made these comments after commencing his duties for the New Year.
en_489741_2	Minister Johnston Fernando mentioned that the stretch of the Southern Expressway was opened because the work had been completed.
en_489741_3	There are many issues in it.
en_489741_4	But he said they expected to complete the entire work of the Expressway from Matara to Hambanthota during the first quarter of this year.
en_489741_5	He revealed that it is intended to declare open the Expressway before the Sinhala and Tamil New Year.
